# Models

Read [app/models/AGENTS.md](../../app/models/AGENTS.md), [docs/ARCHITECTURE.md](../../docs/ARCHITECTURE.md), and [docs/TESTING.md](../../docs/TESTING.md).

- Strict TDD: update `spec/models/` before or with behavior changes.
- Validations, callbacks, and notification side effects stay in models.
- No service objects unless explicitly requested.
- No migrations unless explicitly requested.
- Do not run commands unless explicitly requested.

